|               |     ProjectionExec: expr=[d_year@7 as prev_year, d_year@0 as year, i_brand_id@1 as i_brand_id, i_class_id@2 as i_class_id, i_category_id@3 as i_category_id, i_manufact_id@4 as i_manufact_id, sales_cnt@8 as prev_yr_cnt, sales_cnt@5 as curr_yr_cnt, sales_cnt@5 - sales_cnt@8 as sales_cnt_diff, sales_amt@6 - sales_amt@9 as sales_amt_diff]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
|               |       CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |
|               |         HashJoinExec: mode=Partitioned, join_type=Inner, accumulator=MinMaxLeftAccumulator, on=[(i_brand_id@1, i_brand_id@1), (i_class_id@2, i_class_id@2), (i_category_id@3, i_category_id@3), (i_manufact_id@4, i_manufact_id@4)], filter=CAST(sales_cnt@0 AS Decimal128(17, 2)) / CAST(sales_cnt@1 AS Decimal128(17, 2)) < Some(900000),23,6, projection=[d_year@0, i_brand_id@1, i_class_id@2, i_category_id@3, i_manufact_id@4, sales_cnt@5, sales_amt@6, d_year@7, sales_cnt@12, sales_amt@13]                                                                                                                              |
